This R script cleans and analyzes Samsung acceleromoter data. The data files from 
https://d396qusza40orc.cloudfront.net/getdata%2Fprojectfiles%2FUCI%20HAR%20Dataset.zip

must be in your working directory. The script:

Gets the original features list
Turns the features into unique names
Gets the subjects
Merges the subjects and the observations
Merges the test and training data
Merges the activity ids (y_all) with the observations(x_all)
Adds the activity_id column to the variable names vector
Assigns the column names to the data
Writes our results to a text file

It requires dplyr.
